<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_EP04_CatsAndDogs_CAP" s="315844">
  <T n="name">0xE2B51DF7<!--String: "Create a Pet"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP04\UI\Tutorial\CAP_Intro_01.png">2f7d0004:00000000:bf7afc6ec7c966c6</T>
      <T n="text">0xCFAA49D1<!--String: "Welcome to The Sims™ 4 Create a Pet!\nThis lesson will give you a quick overview of the features available in Create a Pet. Making a Pet is very similar to making a human Sim - just a touch furrier. For a deeper dive, click on any of the more detailed Create a Pet lessons from the menu."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP04\UI\Tutorial\CAP_Intro_02.png">2f7d0004:00000000:bf7afc6ec7c966c5</T>
      <T n="text">0x1DA82C78<!--String: "Create a Sim starts you off with a premade human Sim. To add a cat or a dog to the household, click the Add Sim button to the right of your human Sim's skewer thumbnail."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP04\UI\Tutorial\CAP_Intro_03.png">2f7d0004:00000000:bf7afc6ec7c966c4</T>
      <T n="image_console" p="InEP04\UI\Tutorial_controller\CAP_Intro_03_controller.png">2f7d0004:00000000:3c392860e6113f8f</T>
      <T n="text">0x1DA82C7B<!--String: "Choose the specific breed you had in mind from the Breed catalog or play around with making a Mix Breed! Or just click away at the Randomize button in the bottom of the screen to see what kind of pets come your way."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP04\UI\Tutorial\CAP_Intro_04.png">2f7d0004:00000000:bf7afc6ec7c966c3</T>
      <T n="text">0x1DA82C7A<!--String: "Now for the fun part: start customizing! Just like human Sims, you can directly modify the shape of your pet's body and face by clicking and dragging on the area you want to shape. Change your pet's fur length, ears, or coat markings from the options offered in the arc menu's catalogs. Did we mention you can also Paint on your pet or dress them in cute little outfits? Click on the detailed lessons in the menu for more info!"--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
